OpenCamp

An open source version of Basecamp© built in CakePHP.
Help is welcomed with this project so please branch the code.

WARININGS:
* There are bugs!
* Not tested in any other browser other than Chrome.
* There are some caching issues, might be best to turn them off for now
* Privacy, security and permissions not fully tested

Licencing hasn't been sorted yet but you cannot do the following without my permission:
* Sell or resell this software
* Sell a paid hosting service with this software

We are phasing the development into the following:

Phase One, Basic clone
- Most of the functionality of BC
- Design similar to BC
- Standardised elements
- Appearance for changing schemes
- Projects, overview, milestones, todo, permissions, search
- ACL
- Cross browser testing
- No file sharing
- No email piping, emails only outgoing
- No whiteboard or time

Phase Two, Clone
- Basic administration system
- Categorising content
- Javascript / ajax elements
- File sharing
- Email piping into system for incoming email
- RSS Feeds
- iCalendar feed
- Email updates

Phase Three, BC
- Full system API including interfaces for BC format
- Export
- Import including from BC

Phase Four, Improvements
- Clean up of any draft/rough code
- Theming
- Better UI for people/company permissions
- Improved paginated overview pages
- Search element for RHS
- Full administration area

Phase Five, Beyond!
- Plugins with configration options
- Advanced ACL system

Future
- Move functionality to extendable plugins
- Whiteboard plugin
- Chat plugin
- Mantis / bug tracker items
- Public project lists
- Pages plugin
- Google wave?


Ideas and some old project files at:
https://docs.google.com/leaf?id=0B-rIg4LHA-zaZmUzZGQzYWQtYTdkYy00NWUyLWI0OGItMzdiY2JkZmNjNDAy&hl=en


